==English==

===Adverbial phrase===
'''[[cold]] [[turkey]]'''

# {{idiom}} Not [[gradual]]ly; all at once.  Refers especially to [[quitting]] a [[habit]] by force of will rather than by a gradual reduction.
#: ''It is difficult, but possible to quit smoking '''cold turkey'''.''

